section: Discussion Notes
text: Query caching should use Redis Cluster with fallback to in-memory LRU. Omar to spike Redis Sentinel configuration by 2026-06-28.
quote: "We need to ship the caching layer before the marketing campaign launches in August." — Ahmed
text: Sara raised concern about RSC bundle size; agreed to measure before/after with Lighthouse.

